INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('716eb245a806', '西双版纳一张图二期项目交接', '西双版纳项目交接', '# 资料文件\r\n\r\n## 项目使用的地址\r\n名称 | 地址| 备注\r\n------- | -------  | ------- \r\ngit | https://cowork.sucsoft.com:3443/app2/epbgis-xsbn.git | \r\n大气数据 | http://61.166.240.109:6013/YNSAS/ | \r\n医疗废物文件 | http://61.166.240.109:7320/yngf/appportal.jsp?sysid=yewubanli | 用户名密码bnmcw，mcw2127435 \r\n行政处罚 | https://hbj.xsbn.gov.cn/331.news.list.dhtml | \r\n阿里短信| https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/101300.html?spm=a2c4g.11174283.3.2.8d482c42bljpCY | 3dVRI58mTNwRfE1SlCVi88vELmP8s4\r\n项目外网地址 | http://183.224.196.212:9998/login |\r\n\r\n## 服务器与数据库\r\n说明 | 备注\r\n------- | ------- \r\n版纳服务器 | 183.224.196.212:9389（用户名：administrator 密码：****j@cgrj&yjg2018）\r\n版纳数据库地址| 远程183.224.196.212:9389后再进行远程192.168.0.254（用户名：Administrator 密码：****@cgrj&yjg15）（bnhbyzt2 bnhbyzt2）\r\n杭州内网服务器 | 192.168.80.56（用户名：root 密码：5tgbNHY^）\r\n内网数据库 | 172.18.21.27:1521:ORCL（bnhbyzt bnhbyzt）\r\n版纳dc | http://192.168.0.250:6062/dc-server/login.jsp （admin admin）\r\n内网dc | http://172.18.61.192:6060/dc-server/login.jsp （admin admin）\r\n\r\n- 注：plsql连接内网\r\n```js\r\nFIVEWATER =\r\n  (DESCRIPTION =\r\n    (ADDRESS_LIST =\r\n      (ADDRESS = (PROTOCOL = TCP)(HOST = 172.18.21.27)(PORT = 1521))\r\n    )\r\n    (CONNECT_DATA =\r\n      (SERVICE_NAME = orcl)\r\n    )\r\n  )\r\n```  \r\n\r\n## 文件地址\r\n说明 | 地址\r\n----- | -----\r\njar包部署地址 | D:\\CG\\bnyzt\r\n临时文件地址 | D:\\CG\\bnyzt\\upload\r\napp地址 | D:\\CG\\bnyzt\\upload\\apk\r\n行政处罚文件地址地址 | D:\\CG\\bnyzt\\upload\\punish\r\n\r\n> 注：系统河流图片打包在..\\src\\main\\resources\\static\\images\\admin\\river内\r\n\r\n</br>\r\n\r\n# 代码逻辑\r\n\r\n## 短信验证\r\n### 权限整合\r\n- 配置springboot\r\n\r\n```js\r\n#开启短信验证功能\r\napp.sms.userSmsVerification=true\r\n\r\n#短信配置\r\napp.sms.accessKeyId=LTAI1tcbOm760geM\r\napp.sms.accessKeySecret=3dVRI58mTNwRfE1SlCVi88vELmP8s4\r\napp.sms.templateCode=SMS_151576311\r\napp.sms.endpointName=cn-hangzhou\r\n```  \r\n\r\n- 自定义url规则\r\n\r\n后端（com.sucsoft.dlxxserver.authenticate.**CustomizeWebAuthenticationDetails**）使用`token`字段接受参数，选择对应的验证方式\r\n```java\r\n    /**\r\n     * 短信验证通道\r\n     */\r\n    public static final String SMS_VERIFICATION = \"smsVerification\";\r\n    /**\r\n     * 密码验证通道\r\n     */\r\n    public static final String PASSWORD = \"password\";\r\n```  \r\n前端在登录方法中添加hidden表单项（`templates/login.html`）\r\n```html\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"token\" value=\"password\"/>\r\n  //或是\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"token\" value=\"smsVerification\"/>\r\n```  \r\n> 注意此处后台已将该逻辑注释，见com/sucsoft/dlxxserver/authenticate/**CustomizeAuthenticationProvider.java:47**\r\n\r\n### 资料\r\n- maven\r\n```xml\r\n<dependency>\r\n            <groupId>com.aliyun</groupId>\r\n            <artifactId>aliyun-java-sdk-core</artifactId>\r\n            <version>3.3.1</version>\r\n        </dependency>\r\n        <dependency>\r\n            <groupId>com.aliyun</groupId>\r\n            <artifactId>aliyun-java-sdk-dysmsapi</artifactId>\r\n            <version>1.0.0</version>\r\n        </dependency>\r\n```  \r\n\r\n- github地址：https://github.com/aliyun/aliyun-openapi-java-sdk/tree/master/aliyun-java-sdk-core?spm=a2c4g.11186623.2.12.4e3250a46ICXVP\r\n\r\n- api地址：https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/101300.html?spm=a2c4g.11174283.3.2.8d482c42bljpCY\r\n\r\n## 接口加密\r\n### 后台配置\r\n - 配置properties\r\n```js\r\n#加密密钥，16位\r\napp.encrypt.key=abcdef0123456789\r\n#debug开关，如果为true，则不进行加密\r\napp.encrypt.debug=true\r\n```\r\n - 启动类上添加加密配置`@EnableEncrypt`\r\n```java\r\n@SpringBootApplication(exclude = {LiquibaseAutoConfiguration.class, HibernateJpaAutoConfiguration.class, DataSourceAutoConfiguration.class})\r\n@EnableEncrypt\r\npublic class Application {\r\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\r\n        SpringApplication.run(Application.class, args);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    @Bean\r\n    public EmbeddedServletContainerCustomizer containerCustomizer() {\r\n        return container -> container.setSessionTimeout(24 * 60 * 60);//单位为S,有效期一天\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n - 加密方式：如果对Controller整体加密，则在Controller类上添加`@Encrypt`;多单独某个接口加密，则加在方法上\r\n \r\n> 注：为了简化操作，在加密拦截处s使用以下逻辑。\r\n```java\r\nboolean encrypt = false;\r\n//如果添加了Encrypt注解，且没有使用UnEncrypt注解，并关闭加密Debug模式，则对数据加密\r\nif (returnType.getMethod().isAnnotationPresent(GetMapping.class) \r\n        && !returnType.getMethod().isAnnotationPresent(UnEncrypt.class) \r\n        && !encryptProperties.isDebug()) {\r\n    encrypt = true;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n> 注：为了方便前端的统一拦截，使用了eTag响应头 `response.getHeaders().setETag(\"\\\"encrypt\\\"\");`\r\n如果eTag = \"encrypt\"，则认为是加密的接口\r\n \r\n - 不加密方式：如果再加密类中，又不需要加密的方法，需要使用`@UnEncrypt`注解\r\n - 参数加密：**未处理**\r\n\r\n### 前端使用\r\n\r\n - 统一拦截\r\n```js\r\n// 对加密接口做统一处理\r\n\'response\': function (response) {\r\n    // 如果Http请求头etag是\"encrypt\"，并开启加密模式，则需要做RES解密\r\n    //FIXME if条件中还需要从后台接口中判断是否开启了加密模式，如果没开启，不需要做解密\r\n    if (response.headers().etag === \'\"encrypt\"\') {\r\n        //获取服务器RSA公钥  接口地址：/public/rsaPublicKey\r\n        var serverPublicKey = \"MIGfMA0GCSqGSIb3DQEBAQUAA4GNADCBiQKBgQCNjogbU2HpZ6ifHb4jpXiVS2ka6JlxNd0AgWjnE1xGv0TeJKB9vaXk2rWJ7L9HM3SCiJ8Ackq8hHhNbxXtGIW2MQwNCgHz07Jv0QT4WBolYj1zq8StDEsLxtpkRZlnAFmzYEYqlJ5ukc14GBuB4tB719XzQR1kZugoQxrvCooSHwIDAQAB\";\r\n\r\n        //客户端公私钥\r\n        var clientPublicKey = \"MIGfMA0GCSqGSIb3DQEBAQUAA4GNADCBiQKBgQCZrzFdoIU4GtXKPAv/sHqF1ACVZPoiQw2Nkrf59rQHZqd6+cEbe9DOa5zJWcY38LyItK97htjptRp1lRnla3CEK1RVwPIrsarEK3EEiUGBJnT5UYdAgxD5wMefpjVM6hjT9LPejOVIE7CtN2vfXj8Vs5zYYG6H5fP8YQ7bHZYLLwIDAQAB\";\r\n        var clientPrivateKey = \"\";\r\n\r\n        var encrypt = new JSEncrypt();\r\n        //用服务器公钥对客户端公钥加密\r\n        encrypt.setPublicKey(serverPublicKey);\r\n        var length = clientPublicKey.length;\r\n        //RSA分段加密\r\n        var encryptedData = \'\';\r\n        if (length > 100) {\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < length / 100; i++) {\r\n                encryptedData += encrypt.encrypt(clientPublicKey.substring(i * 100, 100 + (i * 100)));\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        console.log(encryptedData);\r\n\r\n        //获取加密后的AES密钥 接口地址 /public/aesKey?clientPublicKey=xxx\r\n        var aesEncryptedKey = \"UnZVAmG7VYr42dZ5wd964/VCQQ5Gm6t+aELTKTNN0ykmSGUZzp9NGYCnNF3IMOyxvGH9yBfG2ppcU2O36iNJRxEQdy9NlRCDhkbAA3JqssVL2wQcV8PzWZNfpNjbJKV6IG+xo1x0C9ahX8blfFeoSm47GOjJ/XPfQCV+bu4yoVA=\";\r\n        //使用客户端私钥解密\r\n        encrypt = new JSEncrypt();\r\n        encrypt.setPrivateKey(clientPrivateKey);\r\n        var aesKey = encrypt.decrypt(aesEncryptedKey);\r\n        console.log(aesKey);\r\n\r\n        var result = response.data;\r\n\r\n        //16位密钥对应AES-128，接口获取\r\n        var key  = CryptoJS.enc.Utf8.parse(aesKey);\r\n\r\n        //AES解密\r\n        var decrypt = CryptoJS.AES.decrypt(result, key, {\r\n            mode: CryptoJS.mode.ECB,//ECB模式，使用CBC模式，要传vi偏移量\r\n            padding: CryptoJS.pad.Pkcs7//PKCS7Padding与PKCS5Padding相同，后台使用5\r\n        });\r\n\r\n        response.data = JSON.parse(CryptoJS.enc.Utf8.stringify(decrypt).toString());\r\n    }\r\n    return response;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n> 注：\r\n1.此处当字符串过长时，encrypt.encrypt(...)会报错，所以进行了分段加密\r\n2.此处使用的是固定的客户端公私钥、固定的密钥，应当从接口获取\r\n3.获取AES密钥的逻辑应该在登陆后一次查询，不需要每次都查询。\r\n\r\n### 逻辑图\r\n\r\n![alt](http://172.18.61.188:8081/SSMDemo2_img/upload/20190308182613308360016.png)\r\n\r\n![alt](http://172.18.61.188:8081/SSMDemo2_img/upload/20190308182631073574179.png)\r\n\r\n## 在线监控实时数据查询\r\n### 数据库配置\r\n- 分别配置dc库和实时数据库rd库（rd库用户名密码：bnhbrd）\r\n```js\r\ndc.dataset-name=bnyzt_test\r\nrd.dataset-name=bnrd\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 代码配置\r\n- DcConfig配置(com.sucsoft.dlxxserver.config.**DcConfig**)\r\n分别定义数据源，rd为实时数据源\r\n```java\r\n@Value(\"${dc.dataset-name}\")\r\nprivate String dcDataSetName;\r\n@Value(\"${rd.dataset-name}\")\r\nprivate String rdDataSetName;\r\n\r\n//......\r\n\r\n@Primary\r\n@Bean(name = \"dc\")\r\npublic PojoDataset dcDataSet() {\r\n    return this.dataCenter().getPojoDataset(this.dcDataSetName);\r\n}\r\n\r\n@Bean(name = \"rd\")\r\npublic PojoDataset rdDataSet() {\r\n    return this.dataCenter().getPojoDataset(this.rdDataSetName);\r\n}\r\n\r\n@Bean\r\npublic DcTransactionManager dcPojoTransactionManager() {\r\n    return new DcTransactionManager((AbstractDcTransactionalDataset) dcDataSet());\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n - 创建MyUnsafeQueryService类（com.sucsoft.dlxxserver.config.**MyUnsafeQueryService**），与**UnsafeQueryService**做对应，用于查询实时数据。\r\n>  注：需要引用rd的DataSet\r\n    @Autowired\r\n    @Qualifier(\"rd\")\r\n    private PojoDataset dataset;\r\n\r\n - 在CommonService中注入两个查询服务，定义系列查询语句（com.sucsoft.dlxxserver.service.**CommonService**）\r\n > 注：query（...）用于查询普通数据，rdQuery(...)用于查询实时数据。使用时响应的方法即可。\r\n\r\n## AOP功能\r\n- 详见**com.sucsoft.dlxxserver.aop.ControllerAop、com.sucsoft.dlxxserver.domain.ResultBean**\r\n```java\r\n// 已知异常\r\nif (throwable instanceof CheckException) {\r\n    logger.error(signature + \" ===> \" + params + \"  参数校验错误\", throwable);\r\n\r\n    result.setMsg(throwable.getLocalizedMessage());\r\n    result.setCode(ResultBean.PARAM_ERROR);\r\n} else if (throwable instanceof UnloginException) {\r\n    logger.error(\"未登录访问异常  请求IP:\" + ip, throwable);\r\n\r\n    result.setMsg(\"未登录\");\r\n    result.setCode(ResultBean.NO_LOGIN);\r\n} else if (throwable instanceof UnPermissionException) {\r\n    logger.error(\"未授权异常  请求IP:\" + ip);\r\n\r\n    result.setMsg(\"未授权\");\r\n    result.setCode(ResultBean.NO_PERMISSION);\r\n} else if (throwable instanceof QueryException) {\r\n    logger.error(signature + \" ===> \" + params + \"  \" + exceptionMessage, throwable);\r\n\r\n    result.setMsg(\"查询异常:\" + exceptionMessage);\r\n    result.setCode(ResultBean.QUERY_ERROR);\r\n} else if (throwable instanceof OperateException) {\r\n    logger.error(signature + \" ===> \" + params + \"  \" + exceptionMessage, throwable);\r\n\r\n    result.setMsg(\"操作异常:\" + exceptionMessage);\r\n    result.setCode(ResultBean.OPERATE_ERROR);\r\n} else {\r\n    logger.error(point.getSignature() + \" ===> \" + Arrays.toString(point.getArgs()) + \"  未知错误\", throwable);\r\n    //TODO 发送未知的异常，应当发送邮件通知或作其他特殊处理\r\n    //sendMailUtil.sendSimpleMail(sendTo, \"程序出错，请注意！！！\", \"请求IP:\" + ip + \"\\n\" + throwable.toString());\r\n\r\n    result.setMsg(throwable.toString());\r\n    result.setCode(ResultBean.FAIL);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n> 此处预先定义语义化的Exception,方便统一处理\r\n \r\n</br>\r\n\r\n# 脚本与备注\r\n## 表记录\r\n```SQL\r\n/*基本信息*/\r\nSELECT * from hl;  --河流\r\n\r\nSELECT * from hldmjcd;  --河流监测点（关联hl）\r\n\r\nSELECT * from yysydjcd;  --饮用水监测点\r\n\r\nSELECT * from hlzd_dbsrsj;  --河流站点日数据\r\n\r\nSELECT * from hlzd_dbsrsjszpj;  --河流站点日数据评价\r\n\r\nSELECT * from yyszd_dbsrsj;  --饮用水站点日数据\r\n\r\nSELECT * from yyszd_rsjszpj; --饮用水站点日数据评价\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM zsjcsj;  --噪声监测数据\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM zsjcd;  --噪声监测点\r\n\r\n\r\n/*污染源*/\r\nSELECT * from gyqy;  --工业企业\r\n\r\nSELECT * from xqyz;  --畜禽养殖\r\n\r\nSELECT * from wsclc;  --污水处理厂\r\n\r\nSELECT * from shljclc;  --生活垃圾处理厂\r\n\r\n\r\n/*在线监控*/\r\nSELECT * from gdjcsb;  --固定监测设备\r\n\r\nSELECT * from dbswr; --地表水污染\r\n\r\nSELECT * from fspk;  --废水排口\r\n\r\nSELECT * from dqwr;  --大气污染\r\n\r\nSELECT * from fqpk;  --废气排口\r\n\r\nSELECT * from hjktjrelation;  --表关联\r\n\r\n/*业务监管*/\r\nSELECT * FROM jsxm_jh; --项目建设\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM spsb;  --视频监控\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM xzcf; --行政处罚\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM yyxx;  --医院信息\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM ylfw;  --医疗废物\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM lscj; --绿色创建\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM stxz; --生态乡镇\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM xcjc;  --现场监察\r\n\r\n\r\n/*多规合一*/\r\nSELECT * FROM dghy; --多规合一\r\n\r\n/*其他*/\r\nSELECT * FROM file_info;  --文件（apk文件）\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM userlog; --用户日志\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM sms; --短信\r\n\r\n\r\n/*authox*/\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxUser;  --用户表\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxOperation;  --操作\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxObjectOp;  --权限操作\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxgroup;\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxobject;  --权限\r\nSELECT * FROM persistent_logins;\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxsubjecttag;\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxRule;  --角色对应权限\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxRoleinh;\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxRole;  --角色\r\nSELECT * FROM authoxRoleMap;\r\nSELECT * FROM databasechangelog;\r\nSELECT * FROM databasechangeloglock;\r\n```\r\n## 脚本\r\n### 获取表备注\r\n```SQL\r\n-- 查询取表注释\r\nSELECT a.column_name,\r\n       a.comments\r\n  FROM user_col_comments a\r\n INNER JOIN user_tab_columns b\r\n    ON (a.table_name = b.table_name AND a.column_name = b.column_name)\r\n WHERE a.table_name = upper(\'gyqy\')\r\n ORDER BY b.column_id\r\n\r\n--添加表注释\r\nDECLARE\r\n  tab_name VARCHAR2(50) := \'dghy_dwm\';  -- 需要记录备注的表\r\nBEGIN\r\n  FOR info IN (SELECT objectname n,\r\n                      m_alias    v\r\n                 FROM metadataelement\r\n                WHERE objectid IN\r\n                      (SELECT relationid\r\n                         FROM metarelation\r\n                        WHERE relationtype = \'MetaDataElement\'\r\n                          AND objectid = (SELECT objectid FROM metadataentity WHERE objectname = \'dghy_dwm\'))) LOOP\r\n  \r\n    BEGIN\r\n      EXECUTE IMMEDIATE \'comment on column \' || tab_name || \'.\' || info.n || \' is \'\'\' || info.v || \'\'\'\';\r\n    EXCEPTION\r\n      WHEN OTHERS THEN\r\n        NULL;\r\n    END;\r\n  \r\n  END LOOP;\r\nEND;\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 生成dc的xml配置\r\n```SQL\r\n/* 生成xml */\r\nSELECT \'<property name=\"\' || lower(a.column_name) || \'\" type=\"\' || (CASE b.data_type\r\n         WHEN \'VARCHAR2\' THEN\r\n          \'string\'\r\n         ELSE\r\n          (CASE\r\n            WHEN b.data_length < 10 THEN\r\n             \'int_32\'\r\n            WHEN b.data_length < 19 THEN\r\n             \'int_64\'\r\n            ELSE\r\n             \'decimal\'\r\n          END)\r\n       END) || \'\">\r\n            <property-mapping column=\"\' || a.column_name || \'\"/>\r\n        </property>\'\r\n  FROM user_col_comments a\r\n INNER JOIN user_tab_columns b\r\n    ON (a.table_name = b.table_name AND a.column_name = b.column_name)\r\n WHERE a.table_name = upper(\'ylfw\')\r\n   AND lower(a.column_name) NOT IN (\'objectid\', \'objectname\', \'body\', \'m_alias\')\r\n ORDER BY b.column_id;\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 生成javaBean配置\r\n```SQL\r\n/* 生成java类 */\r\nSELECT nvl2(a.comments,\r\n            \'\r\n    @ApiModelProperty(\"\' || a.comments || \'\")\', NULL) || \'\r\n    private \' || (CASE b.data_type\r\n                          WHEN \'VARCHAR2\' THEN\r\n                           \'String\'\r\n                          ELSE\r\n                           (CASE\r\n                             WHEN b.data_length < 10 THEN\r\n                              \'Integer\'\r\n                             WHEN b.data_length < 19 THEN\r\n                              \'Long\'\r\n                             ELSE\r\n                              \'BigDecimal\'\r\n                           END)\r\n                        END) || \' \' || lower(a.column_name) || \';\'\r\n  FROM user_col_comments a\r\n INNER JOIN user_tab_columns b\r\n    ON (a.table_name = b.table_name AND a.column_name = b.column_name)\r\n WHERE a.table_name = upper(\'gyqy\')\r\n   AND lower(a.column_name) NOT IN (\'objectid\', \'objectname\', \'body\', \'m_alias\')\r\n ORDER BY b.column_id;\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 查询关联关系\r\n```SQL\r\n /*查询关联关系*/\r\n SELECT objectid\r\n   FROM hjktjrelation t\r\n  WHERE t.objecttype = \'gyqy\'\r\n    AND t.relationtype = \'spsb\'\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 项目说明\r\n\r\n## 模块\r\n模块 | 别名 \r\n------- | ------- \r\n地表水环境 | Dbs \r\n大气环境 | Dq\r\n污染源 | Wry\r\n业务监管| Business\r\n\r\n接口测试地址：[Swagger](http://localhost:9090/swagger-ui.html)\r\n\r\n## 注意事项\r\n- 接口规范\r\n\r\n接口返回数据皆使用统一处理，形如：\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n	\"msg\": \"success\",\r\n	\"code\": 1,\r\n	\"data\": [\r\n        {\r\n          \"SZQY\": \"景洪市\"\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          \"SZQY\": \"勐海县\"\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          \"SZQY\": \"勐腊县\"\r\n        }\r\n      ]\r\n}	\r\n```  \r\n其中`data`为后台返回的数据，有则返回json信息，无数据或抛出异常，则返回`null`。\r\n\r\n`msg`为后台返回的响应返回信息，默认为`success`。\r\n\r\n`code`为响应返回码，默认为`1`，含义如下：\r\n\r\n返回码 | 含义 | 返回信息  \r\n------- | ------- | -------  \r\n1 | 请求成功| `success`  \r\n0 | 请求失败(未处理的异常) | 异常堆栈错误信息  \r\n-1 | 参数校验异常（如必输信息未输入） | 参数校验错误信息，前台直接输出  \r\n-2 | 查询异常（后台查询语句出错）|   `查询异常`\r\n-3 | 未登录异常| `未登录`\r\n-4 | 未授权异常| `未授权`\r\n-5 | 操作异常| `操作异常`\r\n\r\n', null, '/upload/20190308170820468161782.png', '1552036251523', '1552296041531', '0', '1', '27', '0', '1', '1', '5f01e7e8b32a4c96b7e128cf04e86353', '0', '15551', '1');
